'''苏珊·班尼特'''（{{lang-en|Susan {{abbr|C.|Ciria}} Bennett}}，{{bd|1949年|}}）是一名[[美国|美国]][[配音員|配音員]]，知名於被媒体广泛地报道她曾經为[[美国|美国]][[苹果公司|苹果公司]]所推出的[[iPhone_4S|iPhone 4S]]上的个人语音助理[[Siri|Siri]]的[[美国英语|美国英语]]女声配音。<!--She is most known for being the female {{tsl|en|Americans|American}} voice of {{tsl|en|Apple Inc.|Apple}}'s {{tsl|en|Siri}} since the service was introduced on the iPhone 4S on October 4, 2011.-->

==教育==
班尼特曾就读于[[纽约州|纽约州]][[克林頓縣_(紐約州)|克林顿縣]]的克林顿中央学校，接着就读[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]，在那里她是一名爵士乐队的成员，之后也曾在[[伯克利音乐学院|伯克利音乐学院]]求学。<ref>{{cite web|title=Siri小姐的廬山真面目！|url=http://www.fankudo.com/zombie/12056|publisher=粉酷多|accessdate=2013-10-08}}</ref><!--Bennett attended [http://www.ccs.edu/ Clinton Central School] in Clinton NY and then went on to attend [[Brown_University|Brown University]] where she was a member of a jazz band.  She performed in additional groups as well, one located at the [[Berklee_School_of_Music|Berklee School of Music]].-->

==职业生涯==
於1974年，班尼特意外成为配音女演员，当时她为{{tsl|en|First National Bank of Atlanta||亚特兰大第一国民银行}}录制的录音成为了“提款機蒂莉（Tillie the All-Time Teller）”——世界上第一台[[ATM|ATM]]的提示语音。<!--Bennett became a voice-over actress by accident in the 1970s when she was recorded as the voice of {{tsl|en|First National Bank of Atlanta}}'s "Tillie the All-Time Teller," the first [[ATM|ATM]].--><ref> {{cite news | first = Daniel | last = Cooper | title = Susan Bennett confirms that she is the original voice of Apple's Siri (video) | date = 2013-10-04 | publisher = AOL Inc. | url = http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/04/apple-siri-susan-bennett/ | work = engadget | accessdate = 2013-10-04}}</ref>

班尼特的声音可以在[[达美航空公司|达美航空公司]]的各种终端、[[广告|广告]]、[[自动取款机|自动取款机]]、{{tsl|en|GPS navigation software||GPS导航软件}}以及 {{tsl|en|Telephony||电话系统}}中被发现用作{{tsl|en|public address system||公共广播系统}}语音提示。<!--Bennett can be found as the {{tsl|en|public address system}} voice in various [[Delta_Air_Lines|Delta Air Lines]] terminals, [[commercials|commercials]], [[automated_teller_machine|automated teller machine]]s, {{tsl|en|GPS navigation software}}--><ref> {{cite news | first = John | last = Boone | title = Meet Siri: Susan Bennett Reveals Herself as the Mysterious Voice Behind the iPhone | date = 2013-10-04 | publisher = E! Entertainment Television, LLC. | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/466844/meet-siri-susan-bennett-reveals-herself-as-the-mysterious-voice-behind-the-iphone | work = [[E!|E!]] | accessdate = 2013-10-04}}</ref><!--, and {{tsl|en|Telephony|phone systems}}.--><ref name="CNN"> {{cite news | first = Jessica | last = Ravitz | title = 'I'm the original voice of Siri' | date = 2013-10-04 | publisher = Cable News Network. Turner Broadcasting System, Inc. | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2013/10/04/tech/mobile/bennett-siri-iphone-voice/ | work = [[CNN|CNN]] | accessdate = 2013-10-04}}</ref>

===Siri===
2005年6月，一家名叫{{tsl|en|Nuance Communications|ScanSoft}}的软件公司开始为一个涉及语言建设项目的数据库寻找合适的人声。最终ScanSoft公司通过{{tsl|en|GM Voices}}找到班尼特。2005年7月，她在一个月内每天在家庭录音室中工作四个多小时，来录制包括短语和句子，当时距离iPhone 4S上市还有6年的时间<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.mydrivers.com/1/277/277770.htm | title=她就是苹果Siri的真身 | date=2013-10-05 | agency=驱动之家 | accessdate=2013-10-08 | author=萧萧}}</ref>。这些录音片段再[[串接|串连]]成各种单词、句子和段落并在Siri中被使用<ref name="CNN" />。
<!--In June 2005, a software company by the name of {{tsl|en|Nuance Communications|ScanSoft Inc.}} was looking for someone to be the voice for a database project involving speech construction. Scansoft reached out to {{tsl|en|GM Voices}} and picked Bennett and she worked more than four hours each day for a month in a home recording booth reading phrases and sentences. The recordings were then [[concatenated|concatenated]] into various words, sentences, and paragraphs used in the Siri voice.-->

直到2011年11月，一个朋友通过邮件联系她向她询问iPhone广告中Siri的声音是否是她的时，班尼特才意识到她自己可能是“Siri的声音”。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.k618.cn/bbst/201310/t20131006_3982168.html | title=Siri美国女声完全不知语音被使用 | publisher=www.k618.cn | date=2013-10-06 | accessdate=2013-10-08 | author=孙晓清 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015075457/http://news.k618.cn/bbst/201310/t20131006_3982168.html | archive-date=2013-10-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><!--Bennett became aware she was the voice of Siri when a friend contacted her through email in October of 2011.-->虽然苹果公司至今尚未公开承认班尼特就是Siri的真声，但[[CNN|CNN]]所聘请的专家进行音频取证后作出了100%的把握证明，班尼特和Siri是相同的声音<ref>{{cite web | url=http://tw.tech.yahoo.com/news/siri-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%BB%E7%8F%BE%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E8%98%87%E7%8F%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AC%B8-032010919.html | title=Siri 人妻現真身，原來是蘇珊大嬸～ | publisher=癮科技 | date=2013年10月5日 上午11:20 | accessdate=2013-10-08}}</ref><!--Audio-forensics experts hired by [[CNN|CNN]] proved to a 100 percent certainty that Bennett and Siri are the same voice.--><ref name="CNN" />。

